headline.main: U.S. Military Deploys Forces in Manbij as 'Visible Sign of Deterrence'
headline.print_headline: U.S. Military Deploys Forces in Manbij as 'Visible Sign of Deterrence'

lead_paragraph: The U.S. military has deployed a small number of forces in and around the Syrian city of Manbij to ensure that the different parties do not attack each other and stay focused on fighting the Islamic State militant group, a Pentagon spokesman said on Monday.
